{"color":"DEFAULT","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"Double Jump: Whenever you learn this ability you acquire an invisible frame that checks wether you are jumping or not, \nso that if you are, after pressing space again makes you cast a Leap ability.\n\nSprint: While channeling, every 0.1 second some \"sprint energy\" is drained and \"sprint regeneration\" does not go through\n(it keeps ticking, but the ticks do nothing). \n\tBaseline, you have 100 sprint energy, it drains at 10 energy per second and regenerates at 7 per second.\n\tThe UI (horizontal bar below character) would pop up with a quick fade in animation. The bar would stay until fully\n\t\trecharged, when it would shine briefly to signal its completion and fade out shortly afterwards.\n\tYou can Sprint before fully regenerated, but never when below 15%.\n\n","title":"double jump and sprint","userEditedTimestampUsec":1657102976407000,"createdTimestampUsec":1657102968711000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Double Jump: Whenever you learn this ability you acquire an invisible frame that checks wether you are jumping or not,&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">so that if you are, after pressing space again makes you cast a Leap ability.<\/span><\/p><br /><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Goo